# HappyNest — Blanc Belle: Environment Variables
# Copy this file to .env.local and fill in your values.

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Analytics (optional — booking events are fired automatically)
# Connect Google Tag Manager or GA4 to receive the events below:
#
#   booking_section_viewed      — section scrolled into view
#   booking_form_started        — user begins filling the form
#   booking_form_submitted      — user clicks submit
#   booking_whatsapp_launched   — WhatsApp tab opened
#   booking_lead_saved          — lead written to CSV successfully
#   booking_lead_failed         — CSV write failed (WhatsApp still opens)
#
# Add GTM or GA4 snippet in app/layout.tsx to activate tracking.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# No required env vars for the current booking setup.
# The CSV is written to data/leads.csv on the server at runtime.
